creator: Post Track
descriptionHtml:
Post Track is a universal package tracking system including a set of free features and services:

* Package Tracking;
* Package Manager;
* Package Status Notification.

Both shopping list and delivery status are always kept handy on your computer or mobile device. It is important to be aware of where your package located and we will be glad to assist in shipments' search and managing.


Package Tracking System

The tracking system identifies Post or delivery service by a tracking number automatically. The system helps to track the parcel from the very beginning to the addressee's door.


Package Manager

Nowadays there is no need to track parcels on various websites. The whole information is stored in the user's Package Manager account, being synchronized on all devices of the registered user.


Package Tracking Notifications System

The notification system informs customers about the latest data about the parcel route. Users are notified of both status and current location of the package via e-mail and push-notifications.


App Feature:

* Account manager (login by Facebook, Google);
* Parcel manager (40 active parcels)
* Autodetect carrier by tracking number;
* Auto-translate a tracking status (more 80 languages);
* Bulk parcel tracking;
* Sync account on other devices;
* Push notifications;
* Share a parcel tracking data;
* Parcel archive;
* Dark mode;
* Full carrier information (site, e-mail, phone);
* QR parcel scanner;
* Deals.

descriptionHtml:
Post Track is a universal package tracking system including a set of free features and services:

* Package Tracking;
* Package Manager;
* Package Status Notification.

Both shopping list and delivery status are always kept handy on your computer or mobile device. It is important to be aware of where your package located and we will be glad to assist in shipments' search and managing.


Package Tracking System

The tracking system identifies Post or delivery service by a tracking number automatically. The system helps to track the parcel from the very beginning to the addressee's door.


Package Manager

Nowadays there is no need to track parcels on various websites. The whole information is stored in the user's Package Manager account, being synchronized on all devices of the registered user.


Package Tracking Notifications System

The notification system informs customers about the latest data about the parcel route. Users are notified of both status and current location of the package via e-mail and push-notifications.


App Feature:

* Account manager (login by Facebook, Google);
* Parcel manager (40 active parcels)
* Autodetect carrier by tracking number;
* Auto-translate a tracking status (more 80 languages);
* Bulk parcel tracking;
* Sync account on other devices;
* Push notifications;
* Share a parcel tracking data;
* Parcel archive;
* Dark mode;
* Full carrier information (site, e-mail, phone);
* QR parcel scanner;
* Deals.
